REFRESH RATE: Smooth 120Hz refresh rate ensures fluid motion and reduces motion blur during fast-paced content
HDR SUPPORT: HDR10 compatibility provides enhanced contrast and colour depth for a more immersive viewing experience
EYE COMFORT: Reader Mode and Flicker Safe technology help reduce eye strain during extended viewing sessions
CONNECTIVITY: Features HDMI port and comes with a sleek, slim stand base for stable positioning and modern aesthetics', '4.5 out of 5.0', 'Appliances', '2026-06-25T13:58:55.573Z');
